snippet.title: Card Hog Gameplay
snippet.description:
Pig-based dungeon crawler packed with weird creatures, powerful weapons, magical shenanigans and loads of exciting card combinations!

Copy of the game was provided by SnoutUp.
💵--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1163740/Card_Hog/

🖱 --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Always playing/testing the latest games from first impressions, game tips and occasionally walkthroughs. So if your new to the channel don't forget to 👊🏻 the like button and supporting this channel by subscribing.
🎞 --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
